}}</ref> <ref>''Probiotics And Prebiotics: Scientific Aspects'',Gerald W. Tannock, Horizon Scientific Press, 2005, p. 43[http://books.google.fr/books?id=UOvStP6CY70C&lpg=PA43&hl=fr&pg=PA43#v=onepage&q&f=false] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.fr/books?id=UOvStP6CY70C&lpg=PA43&hl=fr&pg=PA43#v=onepage&q&f=false |date=20200703034501 }}</ref> <ref>''doi:10.1099/00207713-45-3-619'' International Journal of Systematic and Evolutionnary Microbiology (IJSEM) July 1995 vol. 45 no. 3 619-620[http://ijs.sgmjournals.org/content/45/3/619.full.pdf+html]{{Dead link|date=2018年8月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。对[[细胞色素|细胞色素]]、[[氧化酶|氧化酶]]及[[过氧化氢酶|过氧化氢酶]]试验阴性，[[甲型溶血性|甲型溶血性]]试验阳性<ref name="EBI">European Bioinformatics Institute:Bacteria Genomes-STREPTOCOCCUS THERMOPHILUS[http://www.ebi.ac.uk/2can/genomes/bacteria/Streptococcus_thermophilus.html] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ebi.ac.uk/2can/genomes/bacteria/Streptococcus_thermophilus.html |date=20130219070439 }}</ref>。不运动，无[[内生孢子|内生孢子]]<ref name="EBI"/>。
该菌是一种[[乳酸菌|乳酸菌]]，在酸奶中可以发现其存在<ref name="EBI"/><ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.edpsciences.org/10.1051/lait:2003031|pages=125–134|title=Article|journal=Le Lait|volume=84|issue=1-2|date=2004-01-01|issn=0023-7302|language=en|accessdate=2018-04-02|doi=10.1051/lait:2003031|author=Pascal Courtin, Françoise Rul|archive-date=2007-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070314192054/http://www.edpsciences.org/10.1051/lait:2003031|dead-url=no}}</ref>。用于与[[保加利亚乳杆菌|保加利亚乳杆菌]]一起发酵生产[[酸奶|酸奶]]<ref>{{cite journal|title=Analysis of Lactobacillus phages and bacteriocins in American dairy products and characterization of a phage isolated from yogurt|pages=2111–2116|issn=0099-2240|journal=Applied and Environmental Microbiology|volume=62|issue=6|date=1996-6|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/8787408|accessdate=2019-02-13|author=A. O. Kiliç, S. I. Pavlova, W. G. Ma, L. Tao|pmid=8787408|pmc=PMC167989|archive-date=2015-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150303185842/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/8787408|dead-url=no}}</ref>。嗜热链球菌可以为保加利亚乳杆菌提供生成[[嘌呤|嘌呤]]所需的[[叶酸|叶酸]]与[[甲酸|甲酸]]<ref>{{cite journal|title=Mixed-Culture Transcriptome Analysis Reveals the Molecular Basis of Mixed-Culture Growth in Streptococcus thermophilus and Lactobacillus bulgaricus|date=2010-12-01|doi=10.1128/aem.01122-10|language=en|journal=Applied and Environmental Microbiology|volume=76|issue=23|url=http://aem.asm.org/content/76/23/7775|pages=7775–7784|issn=0099-2240|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=Sander Sieuwerts, Douwe Molenaar, Sacha A. F. T. van Hijum, Marke Beerthuyzen, Marc J. A. Stevens, Patrick W. M. Janssen, Colin J. Ingham, Frank A. M. de Bok, Willem M. de Vos, Johan E. T. van Hylckama Vlieg|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020181525/https://aem.asm.org/content/76/23/7775|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==用途==
虽然它所属的[[链球菌属|链球菌属]]包含一些致病的链球菌种，但食品工业使用的嗜热链球菌是安全的<ref>Hutkins, Robert. “Streptococcus Thermophilus LMD-9.” JGI Microbes (2002).</ref>。嗜热链球菌还能把牛乳中的[[乳糖|乳糖]]酵解为[[乳酸|乳酸]]，使得对乳糖敏感的人也可以从牛乳中获得营养 <ref>Delcour, J, T Ferain, and P. Hols. “Advances in the Genetics of Thermophilic Lactic Acid Bacteria.” Food Biotechnology 11 (2000): 497-504.</ref>。
早在1900年代，嗜热链球菌就已大量用于乳品行业，用于生产奶酪与酸奶。酸奶、乳酪中含有嗜热链球菌活体成分对人类健康有益<ref>Taylor, John R. and Mitchell, Deborah. The Wonder of Probiotics. New York, NY: St. Martin’s Press, 2007.</ref>。

